  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201606/bb878b79b264467aa14dbd41a2df9fb5.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t在四级作文中，总会遇到让你论证观点的时候，此时，观点论证型作文模板必不可缺。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">观点论证型作文</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>模板一：</strong><br />\n\t①Many examples can be found to prove that_____（观点）.Take_____（例证）as a typical example. Furthermore, ______（进一步论证）.<br />\n\t②It goes without saying that______（反面论证）.What&rsquo;s more,_____（进一步论证）.In conclusion,______（得出结论）.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>模板二：</strong><br />\n\t①However, nowadays, there exist(s) a lot of_____（何种现象）phenomena in our society. For example,______（举例说明）.<br />\n\t②However, I still______（提出观点）because______（说明原因）. For instance,______（举例论证）.<br />\n\t③In conclusion,______（总结全文）.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">俗话说，万事开头难，作文就是四六级的开头，想攻克作文难关嘛？<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/169092?ch_campaign=cls11154&amp;ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=608d13dd\" target=\"_blank\">赶快来向名师请教吧 &gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a class=\"pagesoft_placeholder\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">[课程推荐]</a></p>\n<p>\n\t本文摘自《巅峰训练 四级写作高分特训》</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p783248/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p783248\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p782754/\">斯皮尔伯格哈佛毕业演讲 给毕业生的6个忠告</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p782948/\">快戳：不能再具体的手部词汇大全</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p778947/\">男士必看：5句话绝对不能对女朋友说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p779009/\">20多岁时干过的蠢事 喝醉后乱发朋友圈中枪</a></li><li style=\"m